summary:
...SHEARED TAMMY WILL MOVE AWAY FROM BERMUDA TONIGHT...
 As of 11:00 PM AST Fri Oct 27
 the center of Tammy was located near 32.7, -61.3
 with movement NNW at 5 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 991 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
